Case-expression conversion is complicated enough to have its own
module, @CgCase@.
\begin{code}

cgExpr (StgCase expr live_vars save_vars bndr srt alt_type alts)
  = setSRT srt $ cgCase expr live_vars save_vars bndr alt_type alts
\end{code}


